  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "An ba da lasisin misalan code, JSON Schema, da samfuran manufa masu iya karantawa ta na'ura a ƙarƙashin MIT License sai dai in an bayyana akasin haka. Kuna iya turawa (deploy) su a shafukanku da kanku kyauta.",
