  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "Canza sanarwar hakkoki zuwa kasuwar lasisi mai aiki maimakon yanar gizo mai bi-ne/a'a na buɗe/rufe.",
  "Copied ✓": "An kwafa ✓",
  "Copy": "Kwafa",
  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Daidai matsayi: zayyanannun bincike masu zaman kansu, shawarwarin ka'idoji, da gwajin ƙayyadaddun bayanai buɗaɗɗiya.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "An gyara wani tsohon default: Belgium (BE) yanzu yana haɗuwa da Yaren Holanci maimakon Faransanci — masu magana da Flemish su ne mafi rinjaye a ƙasar (~60%) fiye da masu magana da Faransanci na Walloon (~40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "An gyara wani tsohon default: Kazakhstan (KZ) yanzu yana haɗuwa da Kazakh maimakon Rashanci, yanzu da fassarar Kazakh ta kasance — irin gyara guda da aka yi wa Belgium a baya.",
  "Crawler access rules": "Ƙa'idojin samun damar Crawler",
