  "Data free-riding vs. trillion-dollar AI valuations": "Amfani kyauta na bayanai sabanin darajar AI ta tiriliyan-daloli",
  "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI": "Shugaban DeepMind na kira da a kafa hukumar ƙa'idoji mai zaman kanta don tsara AI na fasahar zamani",
  "Demis Hassabis proposed a FINRA-style regulator for frontier model releases: labs would submit models for review up to 30 days before deployment, voluntary at first, with a path toward mandatory compliance in the US market.": "Demis Hassabis ya gabatar da shawarar ƙirƙirar mai tsara ƙa'ida irin na FINRA don fitowar samfuran AI na fasahar zamani: dakunan gwaje-gwaje za su gabatar da samfuransu don bita har zuwa kwana 30 kafin fitarwa, na son rai a farko, tare da hanya zuwa ga tilastawa a kasuwar Amurka.",
  "Denied": "An Ƙi",
  "Deployable policy starter template": "Samfurin Farawa na Manufa Mai Turawa",
  "Deployable policy starter template at /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — a minimal static site with the full machine-readable layer, ready for Cloudflare Pages or any static host.": "Samfurin farawa na manufa mai turawa a /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — ƙaramin shafi tsayayye tare da cikakken matsayin mai iya karantawa ta na'ura, a shirye don Cloudflare Pages ko kowane mai masaukin shafi tsayayye.",
  "Deploying machine-readable policies on your site": "Turawa da manufofin da za a iya karantawa ta na'ura a shafinku",
  "Disclaimer": "Sanarwar Keɓancewa",
  "Distinct from human UI, SEO, or plain APIs, the AI Ingestion & Capability Layer gives websites a machine-facing architecture: a Manifest Layer (entry points like /llms.txt and /ai/manifest.json), a Corpus Layer (machine-readable knowledge), a Capability Layer (agent-callable tools), and a Governance Layer (provenance, licensing, versioning). Static-first, upgradeable toward APIs and MCP. Note: in this paper AICL names the ingestion architecture; on this site's protocol pages AICL refers to the AI Content Licensing Layer.": "Ya bambanta da UI na ɗan adam, SEO, ko APIs na yau da kullun, AI Ingestion & Capability Layer na baiwa shafukan yanar gizo tsari mai fuskantar na'ura: Matsayin Manifest (wuraren shiga kamar /llms.txt da /ai/manifest.json), Matsayin Corpus (ilimin da za a iya karantawa ta na'ura), Matsayin Capability (kayan aiki da wakili zai iya kira), da Matsayin Governance (tushen bayanai, ba da lasisi, sigogi). Yana farawa tsayayye, mai iya haɓakawa zuwa APIs da MCP. Lura: a wannan takarda AICL yana suna tsarin ingestion; a shafukan ka'idoji na wannan shafi AICL na nufin AI Content Licensing Layer.",
  "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm": "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm",
  "Docs": "Takardu",
  "Docs / Examples": "Takardu / Misalai",
  "Document library": "Ɗakin Adana Takardu",
