  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Nunin ilimi: HMAC-SHA256 tare da asirin da aka raba, yana nuna token ɗin lasisi da aka daure ga takamaiman buƙata, mai ƙarewa, kuma mai tabbatarwa. Ya kamata a sanya wa token na ainihi hannu ta hanyar asymmetric, tare da mabuɗin jama'a na mai bugawa da za a iya samu a ƙarƙashin /.well-known/.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Ƙarin abubuwa takwas na /topics, wannan karon wakilin AI ne ya bincika maimakon a zaɓe su da hannu — ka'ida ɗaya kamar da: an ɗauko kowane tushe kuma an tabbatar da shi yana raye, taƙaitattun bayanai sake-rubutu na asali, kafin a ƙara komai. Jimlar abubuwa 14.",
